@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_unxhqp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.60)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = v0
    v0 = v2
    v0 = 0.86
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 / (v1 + 0.71 + v2 + 0.41)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.83))
    data[tid] = v0
